{"wp_event_id":368604730023922585,"message/api":"anthropic-messages","message/content[0]/type":"thinking","message/content[1]/text":"从 `openclaw status` 可以看到当前 session 的 token 使用情况：\\n\\n```\\n│ agent:main:main │ direct │ just now │ k2p5 │ 34k/262k (13%) · 🗄️ 96% cached │\\n```\\n\\n显示使用了 **34k/262k** tokens（13%），其中 96% 是缓存的。\\n\\n如果你想在聊天中获取更详细的消耗信息，可以使用：\\n\\n```\\n/session_status\\n```\\n\\n或者使用 `/status` 命令，它会显示：\\n- 当前模型\\n- Token 使用量/上下文窗口大小\\n- 使用百分比\\n- 缓存命中率\\n\\nOpenClaw 默认使用 **Kimi k2p5** 模型（上下文窗口 262k），目前似乎没有内置的按模型成本计算功能，主要通过 token 使用量和上下文百分比来监控。","message/content[1]/type":"text","message/model":"k2p5","message/provider":"kimi-coding","message/role":"assistant","message/stopReason":"stop","message/timestamp":1773799782275,"message/usage/cacheRead":37632,"message/usage/cacheWrite":0,"message/usage/cost/cacheRead":0,"message/usage/cost/cacheWrite":0,"message/usage/cost/input":0,"message/usage/cost/output":0,"message/usage/cost/total":0,"message/usage/input":252,"message/usage/output":215,"message/usage/totalTokens":38099,"parentId":"9034d507","timestamp":"2026-03-18T02:09:50.693Z","type":"message","wp_src_key":"file_1","access_source":"../openclaw/target_data/raw_log.dat","biz":"demo","env":"dev"}
